Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: A Brief Joust and Tumble with Sir Galahad
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00szsdf
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 10 Mar 2000
Alistair Cook looks at the rise and fall of Senator John McCain - briefly a challenger to George W Bush to be the Republican party's candidate in the forthcoming election.